title: Ivanka Trump, Mnuchin officially open U.S. embassy in Jerusalem
text:
Ivanka Trump, Mnuchin officially open U.S. embassy in Jerusalem 10:08am EDT - 00:48
The U.S. officially opens its embassy to Israel in Jerusalem, fulfilling President Trump's pledge to recognise the city as Israel's capital. Rough cut (no reporter narration).
